high_descs: Turn right, go to the central counter, and turn left.
Take the sponge from the central counter.
Turn right, go to the end of the central counter, turn left, go to the stove top, and turn right.
Put the sponge in the pan on the stove top.
Take the pan and the sponge from the stove top.
Turn around, go to the central counter, turn left, and turn left.
Open the cabinet next to the stove top, put the pan and the sponge inside the cabinet, and close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan containing a sponge in the cabinet next to the oven.

high_descs: Turn left, move to the island near the dinner plate.
Pick up the sponge from the island.
Turn right, move to in front of the stove.
Put the sponge in the pan on the right side of the stove.
Pick up the right side pan from the stove.
Turn right, move to the counter right of the stove.
Put the pan in the lower cabinet, right of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a sponge in a pan, place the pan in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right and face the counter on the left.
Pick up the sponge off of the counter.
Turn right and go to the stove.
Put the sponge in the pan on the right of the stovetop.
Pick up the pan and sponge from the stove.
Go right to the cupboard.
Open the cupboard and put the pan and sponge inside.
anns.task_desc: Put away the sponge and pan in the cupboard.
